rows.label: qst006101_msg0002
rows.name:
It's about a "Mystery Continent"...
Looks like some kind of fairy tale.

rows.label: qst006101_msg0003
rows.name:
"Long ago, there was a mystical
kingdom in a mysterious continent."

rows.label: qst006101_msg0004
rows.name:
A mysterious continent...a mystical
kingdom... I like the sound of all this.
They sound fitting for my personage.

rows.label: qst006101_msg0005
rows.name:
"But this mysterious continent was
destroyed in a single night."

rows.label: qst006101_msg0006
rows.name:
What?! A single night?!
Can that be possible?

rows.label: qst006101_msg0007
rows.name:
"That mysterious continent of which
nobody knows..."

rows.label: qst006101_msg0008
rows.name:
"Its secrets are inscribed on the
Dalnes Stone in Temperantia."

rows.label: qst006101_msg0011
rows.name:
Hold on. You're not going to just
believe this fairy tale, are you?

rows.label: qst006101_msg0012
rows.name:
You fool! Fairy tales too are legitimate
records of the past!

rows.label: qst006101_msg0013
rows.name:
This message was left for a reason.
It is only right that we investigate!

rows.label: qst006101_msg0014
rows.name:
Now come, my retainers.
We head for Temperantia!
